<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.5.9">
<l>ōti yāyira nāmamum paṇintētti niṉṉaṭain tēṟkoru poruḷ</l>
<l>vētiyā varaiyā vuraiyā yorumāṟṟa mentāy</l>
<l>nīti yākiya vētamā muṉiyāḷar tōṟṟa muraittu maṟṟavark</l>
<l>kātiyā yiruntā yaṇiyāli yammāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For me who takes refuge in you, praising [and] bowing [to you],</l>
<l rend="indent">chanting [your] one-thousand names, learned one, king,</l>
<l>Say [just] one meaning, [just] one word, my father,</l>
<l>Lord of lovely Āli, you who are the first of others,</l>
<l rend="indent">having [fore]told of the appearance</l>
<l>Of the great sages of the righteous Vedas.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
